game starts w/ all four players at the top (display name and health)

player selects enemy to fight, then defeat all remaining fighters
	player chooses characters by clicking on their picture
	once selected, enemy moves to defender area
	once defeated, the enemy must move to different part of the screen
player attacks by clicking attack button
	each attack damages the enemy
	enemy immediately launches counterattack and damages player
player wins by defeating all enemies, loses when its hp goes to 0


characters have attributes
	health points, attack power, counter attack power
	all characters attributes must differ 
when player attacks, its attack power increases by its base attack power
enemy character only has counter attack power which remains constant
characters cannot recover hp
player should be able to win no matter what character they choose



THEME: monty python and the holy grail